name: The First Flight V1
description:
The First Flight

In history, it is believed that after the floods covered earth Noah sent out a raven, and it kept flying back and forth until the water had dried up from the earth.
Noah picked the Raven to be the first out of the Ark, to wander around and ensure it was safe.
This symbolizes the one "protector", a symbol of a leader and the one ahead opening path to others.
This design was made by the artist Diego Mendez in 2011, it was intended to be a tattoo, and this is the only design made.
Due to unforeseen circumstances the tattoo was never completed but the design is fully ready.
This NFT gives the rights to the tattoo design along with a certificate of authenticity. 
To ensure the uniqueness of the design only 1 NFT will be minted. 
Version 1 of 3.
